{"tid":2452526,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"鯨落呢首歌D歌詞好凄美","createTime":"2021-03-19T01:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T03:40:26.000Z","uid":1399,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"83f5c3a2f70db7f8283a03ca62dc99f5b0c8c93c","tid":2452526,"uid":1399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T01:35:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Aoz78QeHneQ&amp;ab_channel=WhaleWatchWesternAustralia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAoz78QeHneQ%26ab_channel%3DWhaleWatchWesternAustralia&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSvLVWyXx0XMfrvcdwhNvS5Y%3D&h=5ea85859\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Aoz78QeHneQ&amp;ab_channel=WhaleWatchWesternAustralia</a><br />\n<br />\n虎鯨十分聰明又兇猛！澳洲西海岸一頭長約16公尺的藍鯨，就遭約70頭虎鯨圍殺，被推擠向較淺的大陸棚，最終不敵對方血染海洋。有海洋科學家形容，這是「一場戰略周全的戰役。牠們似乎知道該怎麼做」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://beachgrit.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Screen-Shot-2021-03-18-at-7.27.12-AM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbeachgrit.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2FScreen-Shot-2021-03-18-at-7.27.12-AM.png&h=c86f3347&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5512/5512851.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5512%2F5512851.jpg&h=7bf2970c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據《澳洲廣播公司》報導，海洋科學家布朗（Kirsty Brown）當時搭乘遊船來到事發地，正好見證了這次海洋大戰。她指出，當地是虎鯨、大烏賊、鯊魚和鳥類的聚集處，原本在海中四散的虎鯨，突然像被激怒了一樣，原來是一頭長約16公尺的藍鯨闖入了牠們的領地。<br />\n<br />\n虎鯨們將藍鯨包圍，布朗形容，「這是一場戰略周全、互相合作的戰役，牠們耐心用持久戰，來消滅這頭碩大的藍鯨。」<br />\n<br />\n孤立無援的藍鯨想要逃脫被圍攻的局面，但對手們一次次推擠，硬是阻擋了牠的生路，並逐漸將牠推到較淺的大陸棚，使得逃脫路線不斷縮減。布朗說，「這是牠們的策略，牠們似乎知道該怎麼做。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/iJH1MMpWZj9atg-ok-t475YyE1o=/760x428/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JGROVPO45VHNDA2EUUGLXNCDFU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FiJH1MMpWZj9atg-ok-t475YyE1o%3D%2F760x428%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJGROVPO45VHNDA2EUUGLXNCDFU.jpg&h=421f1de8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/6-fvH1MOuNHJ5zwR1CXsM19YT5w=/760x428/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WAIVFTHCIVD2VOH7FLKKYXM26Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6-fvH1MOuNHJ5zwR1CXsM19YT5w%3D%2F760x428%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWAIVFTHCIVD2VOH7FLKKYXM26Y.jpg&h=1f6b212a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n布朗表示，這場戰鬥持續了有3、4個小時，最後一團鮮血漂浮在海面上，虎鯨們則開始分食戰利品，而諸如海鳥等其他動物也加入瓜分行列；遊客們有的為藍鯨落淚，有的則處於震驚之中，陷入沉默。"},{"pid":"ac93e68d175c0da1982cc71e4fceec07cf07cb3c","tid":2452526,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T01:38:31.000Z","msg":"殺咗之後點？係咪會食咗佢？"},{"pid":"670cbdae21680a06977714a14c1d7196889c9b62","tid":2452526,"uid":1399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac93e68d175c0da1982cc71e4fceec07cf07cb3c","tid":2452526,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T01:38:31.000Z","msg":"殺咗之後點？係咪會食咗佢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T01:46:59.000Z","msg":"布朗表示，這場戰鬥持續了有3、4個小時，最後一團鮮血漂浮在海面上，虎鯨們則開始分食戰利品，而諸如海鳥等其他動物也加入瓜分行列"},{"pid":"0f981ed463a790fdb65f57ea1f588d68a75fb2cf","tid":2452526,"uid":1399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T01:48:15.000Z","msg":"一棵大樹倒下後，會被蜂擁而至的微生物分解，成為大地珍貴的養分。而一隻鯨魚悄然死亡，也會創造出一個複雜的、獨一無二的生態系統。當鯨魚在海洋中死去時，牠的屍體會下沉很長一段距離，至少1000公尺，而這個緩慢的過程，有一個飽含詩意的名字&mdash;鯨落（Whale Fall）。"},{"pid":"169c366082c0e2ab52bb9a3226ff20c7f0fa28d3","tid":2452526,"uid":78039,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T01:49:48.000Z","msg":"沉沒在大海怎配有權被愛 命運若一早記載緣份不再<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" clas